<templates id="template" xml:space="preserve">
    <t t-name="website.social_hover">
        <div class="row clearfix" style='font-size:16px'>
            <div class="col-xs-12 css_editable_mode_hidden">
                <t t-foreach="medias" t-as="media">
                    <a style="cursor: pointer" t-attf-class="fa-stack fa-lg share #{media}">
                        <span class="fa fa-square fa-stack-2x"></span>
                        <span t-attf-class="fa fa-#{media} fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></span>
                    </a>
                </t>
            </div>
        </div>
    </t>

    <t t-name="website.social_question">
        <div class="modal fade" id="social_share_modal">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header alert alert-info'">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">x</span>
                    </button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title">Thanks for posting your question</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>On average, 45% of questions shared on social netwroks get an answer within 5 hours and questions shared on two social networks have 65% more chance to get an answer than not shared questions.</p>
                    <p>Share on:</p>
                    <div class="share-icons">
                        <t t-foreach="medias" t-as="media">
                            <a style="cursor: pointer" t-attf-class="fa-stack fa-lg share #{media}">
                                <span class="fa fa-square fa-stack-2x"></span>
                                <span t-attf-class="fa fa-#{media} fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></span>
                            </a>
                        </t>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-link pull-right" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </t>

    <t t-name="website.social_answer">
        <div class="modal fade" id="social_share_modal">
            <div class="modal-dialog modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header alert alert-info'">
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">x</span>
                    </button>
                    <h4 class="modal-title">Thanks for posting your question</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <p>By sharing you answer, you will get an additionnal 15 karma points if your answer is selected as the right one. See what you can do with karma <a href="https://www.odoo.com/forum/how-to/miscellaneous-14/how-does-karma-work-odoo-v8-forum-software-57845" target="_blank">here</a>.</p>
                    <p>Share on:</p>
                    <div class="share-icons">
                        <t t-foreach="medias" t-as="media">
                            <a style="cursor: pointer" t-attf-class="fa-stack fa-lg share #{media}">
                                <span class="fa fa-square fa-stack-2x"></span>
                                <span t-attf-class="fa fa-#{media} fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></span>
                            </a>
                        </t>
                        <button type="button" class="btn btn-link pull-right" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </t>

    <t t-name="website.social_alert">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
            <h4>This question is no longer part of the top list</h4>
            <p>Share it on social networks in order to improve the chances to get an answer.</p><br/>
            <div style='text-align:center'>
                <t t-foreach="medias" t-as="media">
                    <a style="cursor: pointer" t-attf-class="fa-stack fa-lg share #{media}">
                        <span class="fa fa-square fa-stack-2x"></span>
                        <span t-attf-class="fa fa-#{media} fa-stack-1x fa-inverse"></span>
                    </a>
                </t>
            </div>
        </div>
    </t>
</templates>
